thread.title: California man believed killed near Josephine County lake
thread.title_full: California man believed killed near Josephine County lake | OregonLive.com

author: Elliot Njus | The Oregonian/OregonLive
title: California man believed killed near Josephine County lake
text:
Police are investigation the death of a Crescent City, California, man near Selmac Lake in Josephine County as a homicide.
Josephine County sheriff's deputies found the man, Roger L. Huntington, 43, dead in his black Chevrolet Trailblazer near the lake's boat ramp. A 9-1-1 caller had reported discovering the body.
The Oregon State Police said the death is being investigating as a homicide, but declined to say how Huntington was killed.
The Oregon State Police asked that anyone with information on the case, or who saw Huntington or his vehicle, call the agency's Southern Command Center at 541-776-6111.
-- Elliot Njus
